OL,6,FAt least one in four children are
OL,7,Fliving in poverty in two-thirds of
OL,8,Fparliamentary constituencies, new
OL,9,Fanalysis suggests.
OL,11,FAhead of the General Election, parties
OL,12,Fhave been urged to commit to "systemic
OL,13,Fchanges" to help struggling families.
OL,15,FThese are highest in the North West,
OL,16,Fwhere 90% of constituencies have at
OL,17,Fleast one in four children living in
OL,18,Fpoverty.
