OL,6,FThe two-child limit, introduced under
OL,7,Fthe Conservative Government in 2017,
OL,8,Frestricts Child Tax Credit and
OL,9,FUniversal Credit to the first two
OL,10,Fchildren in most households. It is a
OL,11,Fpolicy charities and campaigners have
OL,12,Frepeatedly said should be scrapped.
OL,14,FLast month, Labour leader Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer said he would scrap the cap
OL,16,F"in an ideal world" but added that "we
OL,17,Fhaven't got the resources to do it at
OL,18,Fthe moment".
